high_descs: Turn and face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the egg from the counter.
Go right and stand to face the microwave.
Put the egg in the microwave, turn it on, take the egg out, and shut the door.
Turn and walk to stand in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the egg on the shelf and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the counter left of the stove
Pick up the egg from the counter
Turn and walk a few feet right then turn left to face the microwave
Cook the egg in the microwave then remove it
Turn and walk to the fridge on your left
Open the fridge  and set the egg inside it
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked egg into the fridge

high_descs: Turn 90 degrees to the left and walk towards the counter.
Turn 90 degrees to the right and turn towards the stove when you reach it.
Open the microwave, place the potato inside, close it, cook the potato, and remove it when it is done cooking.
Turn around 180 degrees and cross the room. Turn 90 degrees to the right when you reach the fridge and walk towards it.
Open the freeze drawer and place the potato inside, closing it after.
anns.task_desc: Take a potato from the count, cook it, finally putting it in the freezer.
